	"zh_TW": {
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.opening_after_storybook.001.lumi.text": "你又在看那本書啊？",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.opening_after_storybook.002.stagedir.text": "Lyra 將書頁輕輕闔上。",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.opening_after_storybook.003.lumi.text": "明明最後都變成泡泡了，為什麼還算 Happy Ending？",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.opening_after_storybook.004.stagedir.text": "Lyra 沒有回答，只是微微笑了一下。",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.opening_after_storybook.005.lumi.text": "你笑什麼啦。",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.opening_after_storybook.005.choice.happy_ending.text": "因為這是 Happy Ending",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.opening_after_storybook.005.choice.because_lumi.text": "因為你在旁邊",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.opening_after_storybook.005.response.happy_ending.001.lumi.text": "喔？你現在會說這種話了喔。",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.opening_after_storybook.005.response.because_lumi.001.lumi.text": "等、等等，這回答也太狡猾了吧。",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.opening_after_storybook.006.lumi.text": "好吧，反正你每次看完都這個表情。",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.opening_after_storybook.007.lumi.text": "咦？",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.opening_after_storybook.008.lumi.text": "地震？快，我們得出去看看！",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.movement_tutorial_after_storybook.001.system.text": "操作說明：使用 WASD 或方向鍵移動，也可以用滑鼠左鍵點擊地面移動。",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.movement_tutorial_after_storybook.002.system.text": "靠近可互動的地方會觸發對話。對話中可以按 Enter 或點擊滑鼠左鍵繼續。",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.storybook_after_reading.001.lumi.text": "你又在看那本啊？",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.storybook_after_reading.002.lumi.text": "明明最後變成泡泡了，為什麼還算 Happy Ending？",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.storybook_after_reading.003.lyra.text": "……",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.storybook_after_reading.004.lumi.text": "你笑什麼啦。",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.storybook_after_reading_again.001.lumi.text": "你已經把那頁看到會背了吧。",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.storybook_after_reading_again.002.lyra.text": "……",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.storybook_after_reading_again.003.lumi.text": "好啦，我知道你喜歡。",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.storybook_after_reading_quiet.001.lumi.text": "這本書明明很舊，但你每次看都很安靜。",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.window.001.lumi.text": "外面的水光今天很安靜。",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.window_lights.001.lumi.text": "遠處的燈好像比平常暗一點。",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.window_surface.001.lumi.text": "你又在想海面上面的事嗎？",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.bookshelf.001.lumi.text": "這裡全都是你反覆看過的書。",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.bookshelf_notes.001.lumi.text": "書頁裡夾著你的筆記。字還是一樣小。",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.bookshelf_old_story.001.lumi.text": "童話書、歷史書、還有一堆看起來很難的書。",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.bed.001.lumi.text": "現在不是睡回籠覺的時候吧？",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.bed_blanket.001.lumi.text": "被子折得很整齊。真難得。",
		"sunken_city_lyra_room.bed_morning.001.lumi.text": "再躺回去的話，我會把你叫起來喔。"
	},
